{"word":"Candlestick","slug":"candlestick","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Candlestick</b> Of the tabernacle:<br/> - Made after divine pattern<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=40'>Exo 25:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=37&verse=24'>Exo 37:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=8&verse=4'>Num 8:4</a> <br/> - Place of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=26&verse=35'>Exo 26:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=25'>Exo 40:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=2'>Heb 9:2</a> <br/> - Furniture of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=38'>Exo 25:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=37&verse=23'>Exo 37:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=10'>Num 4:10</a> <br/> - Burned every night<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=27&verse=21'>Exo 27:21</a> <br/> - Trimmed every morning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=7'>Exo 30:7</a> <br/> - Carried by Kohathites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=4'>Num 4:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=15'>Num 4:15</a> <br/> - Called Lamp of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=3&verse=3'>1Sa 3:3</a> <br/> Of the temple:<br/> - Ten branches of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=50'>1Ki 7:50</a> <br/> - Of gold<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=28&verse=15'>1Ch 28:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=4&verse=20'>2Ch 4:20</a> <br/> - Taken with other spoils to Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=19'>Jer 52:19</a> <br/> Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=4&verse=2'>Zec 4:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=4&verse=11'>Zec 4:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=1&verse=13'>Rev 1:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=1&verse=20'>Rev 1:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=2&verse=5'>Rev 2:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=11&verse=4'>Rev 11:4</a>"}]}